strings: <voice_0x0100165C><center>Did you succeed in collecting all the games?

<voice_0x0100165D><center>Found what I was looking for
<center>and came back late in the evening.

<voice_0x0100165E><center>You cannot hide the truth from me.
<center>You can only see the light in your eyes.
<voice_0x0100165F><center>I want to tell you everything I have...
<voice_0x01001660><center>but I can't

<voice_0x01001661><center>Up to 1 luggage per person is planned.
<center>Accessories can be stowed in the pocket.

<voice_0x01001662><center>It gives you one last hope
<center>to survive in this world.

<voice_0x01001663><center>You found the last hope in this world.
<center>I want to give you...
<voice_0x01001664><se_high>Accuracy: Go now!
<voice_0x01001665><se_low>King of tricks: This is the room of Trodan! Thank you for your interest in this area! Totally fake! Do not touch me!

<voice_0x01001666><center>No need to worry,
<center>Rafson's spirit is no longer in the hall.
<voice_0x01001667><center>There are now seven souls among the saints.

<voice_0x01001668><center>The truth behind this estate
<center>has long been hidden.

<voice_0x01001669><center>Originally made by the Seven Sages
<center>under my leadership.
<voice_0x0100166A><center>they called him
<voice_0x0100166B><center>It is called a bud.

<voice_0x0100166C><center>You will need it to destroy
<center>the dark shields around Lapthorn.

<voice_0x0100166D><center>It becomes brittle only when broken.
<center>This is all you can do.
<voice_0x0100166E><center>i'll take you to his house
<voice_0x0100166F><center>The Dark Lord will fight you to the death...

<voice_0x01001670><center>However, his attack had to be countered
<center>by his team's strength.

<voice_0x01001671><center>Praying for strength, the four of us, one by one,
<center>called upon the spirits of our ancestors
<center>to release the power of the heavens.

<voice_0x01001672><center>I can't give any other advice.
<center>Do you know what to do
<center>when you meet the lord of darkness?
<voice_0x01001673><center>I'll explain it again.

<voice_0x01001674><center>For this reason,
<center>this battle can no longer be postponed.
<center>are you ready
<voice_0x01001675><center>just give me a moment

<voice_0x01001676><center>Now you must fight him.
<center>Better to use a stick.
